$$\ \ \ \ \ \ \ \ \ \ \ \ \ \ \ \ \ Matthews\ Correlation\ Coefficient\ \left({MCC} \right) = {{TP \times TN\ -\ FP \times FN} \over \sqrt {\left({TP + FP} \right) \times \left({TP + FN} \right) \times \left({TN + FP} \right) \times \left({TN + FN} \right)}}$$
